verbose_text: As shown in Figure XREF_FIG A, amine functionalized superparamagnetic iron oxide nanoparticles with a cross linked dextran coating (MN) have been prepared, and a Cy5.5 dye was conjugated to the surface of nanoparticles to produce MN-Cy5.5.
